profile: Creative Concepts Carpentry Inc. in Nanaimo, British Columbia specializes in interior finishing carpentry and woodworking related tasks for your home or business. We are skilled in custom woodwork, cabinetry, door and window installation, counter tops, fireplace mantels, crown moulding, custom ceilings, pillars, arches, flooring, exterior finishing, and siding.
